org.afplib.afplib

Interface WindowSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WindowSpecificationImpl

    public interface WindowSpecification
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Window Specification'.

    The following features are supported:

    • FLAGS
    • RES3
    • CFORMAT
    • UBASE
    • XRESOL
    • YRESOL
    • IMGXYRES
    • XLWIND
    • XRWIND
    • YBWIND
    • YTWIND

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getWindowSpecification()
